Data from my fire footprints

load("~/Shrubs-Seedlings/compiled_data/shrub_growth/My_FireFootprint_data.Rdata")
me <- ht_by_spp

Sync column names

latimer <- latimer %>% 
  mutate(Year_meas = 2018) %>% 
  rename(Year.of.Fire = fire_year, Date = SurveyDate) %>% 
  dplyr::select(Fire, years_since_fire, Year_meas, Year.of.Fire, Shrub_species, shrub_ht) %>% 
  rename(ShrubHt = shrub_ht)
young <- young %>% 
  rename(Shrub_species = dominant_shrub_1) %>% 
  rename(ShrubHt = dominant_shrub_ht_cm) %>% 
  dplyr::select(-Date)

Add column for df_source

young$df_source = "young"
latimer$df_source = "latimer"
welch$df_source = "welch"
me$df_source = "me"

Remove rows in young that are already in welch

young <- anti_join(young, welch, by = c("Year_meas", "Regen_Plot"))
## Warning: Column `Regen_Plot` joining factor and character vector, coercing
## into character vector

Join

df <- full_join(young, latimer)
## Joining, by = c("Fire", "years_since_fire", "Year_meas", "Year.of.Fire", "Shrub_species", "ShrubHt", "df_source")
## Warning: Column `Fire` joining factors with different levels, coercing to
## character vector
## Warning: Column `Shrub_species` joining factors with different levels,
## coercing to character vector
df <- df %>% 
  rename(modal_ht_cm = ShrubHt)
df <- full_join(df, welch)
## Joining, by = c("Regen_Plot", "Fire", "years_since_fire", "Year_meas", "Shrub_species", "modal_ht_cm", "df_source")

Sync shrub species names

df <- df %>% 
  mutate(Shrub_species = 
           case_when(Shrub_species == "ARCPAT" ~ "ARPA6",

Lump ARVI and ARPA

  mutate(Shrub_species =

Plot for all species that are in my data and have at least 5 years of data

over7years <- df %>% 
  select(Shrub_species, years_since_fire) %>% 
  distinct() %>% 
  group_by(Shrub_species) %>% 
  summarize(count = n()) %>% 
  filter(count > 7) %>% 
  filter(Shrub_species != "none")
over7years
## # A tibble: 5 x 2
##   Shrub_species count
##   <chr>         <int>
## 1 ARPA6_ARVI       13
## 2 CECO             13
## 3 CEIN3            11
## 4 CHSE11           10
## 5 RIBES             8
focal_spp <- df %>% 
  filter(df_source == "me") %>% 
  dplyr::select(Shrub_species) %>% 
  distinct()
focal_spp
## # A tibble: 21 x 1
##    Shrub_species
##    <chr>        
##  1 ARPA6_ARVI   
##  2 CECO         
##  3 CEIN3        
##  4 CHSE11       
##  5 CHFO         
##  6 PREM         
##  7 RIRO         
##  8 CEPR         
##  9 Ribes        
## 10 willow       
## # ... with 11 more rows
df_plot <- df %>% 
  filter(Shrub_species %in% over7years$Shrub_species & Shrub_species %in% focal_spp$Shrub_species)
unique(df_plot$Shrub_species)
## [1] "CECO"       "CEIN3"      "CHSE11"     "ARPA6_ARVI"
df_plot <- droplevels(df_plot)
ggplot(df_plot, aes(x = years_since_fire, y = modal_ht_cm))+
  geom_point(aes(shape = df_source, col = Fire))+
  geom_smooth(method = "loess", span = 1)+
  facet_wrap(~Shrub_species, ncol = 2)+
  theme_bw()
